      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Conferences\" title=\"Conferences\">Conferences</a> * Computer and Games 2004</b>\n</p><p><b><a href=\"/CG_2002\" title=\"CG 2002\">&lt; Prev</a> <a href=\"/CG_2006\" title=\"CG 2006\">Next &gt;</a></b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Brain_research_labs-Bar_Ilan_university.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/09/Brain_research_labs-Bar_Ilan_university.jpg/330px-Brain_research_labs-Bar_Ilan_university.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"198\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/09/Brain_research_labs-Bar_Ilan_university.jpg/500px-Brain_research_labs-Bar_Ilan_university.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/09/Brain_research_labs-Bar_Ilan_university.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Brain_research_labs-Bar_Ilan_university.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bar-Ilan_University#Leslie_and_Susan_Gonda_Multidisciplinary_Brain_Research_Center\">Gonda Brain Research Center</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p>The <b>Fourth International Conference on Computers and Games</b> was held at the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bar-Ilan_University#Leslie_and_Susan_Gonda_Multidisciplinary_Brain_Research_Center\">Gonda Brain Research Center</a> of the <a href=\"/Bar-Ilan_University\" title=\"Bar-Ilan University\">Bar-Ilan University</a> in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramat_Gan\">Ramat Gan</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Israel\">Israel</a>, July 5-7, <a href=\"/Timeline#2004\" title=\"Timeline\">2004</a>, in conjunction with the <a href=\"/9th_Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"9th Computer Olympiad\">9th Computer Olympiad</a> and the <a href=\"/WCCC_2004\" title=\"WCCC 2004\">12th World Computer Chess Championship</a> . \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Proceedings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Proceedings</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Lectures\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Lectures</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Photos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Reports\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Reports</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Proceedings\">Proceedings</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CG_2004&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Proceedings\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a>, <a href=\"/Yngvi_Bj%C3%B6rnsson\" title=\"Yngvi Björnsson\">Yngvi Björnsson</a>, <a href=\"/Nathan_S._Netanyahu\" title=\"Nathan S. Netanyahu\">Nathan S. Netanyahu</a> (eds.)</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/book/10.1007%2F11674399\">Computers and Games</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></dd>\n<dd> 4th International Conference, CG 2004</dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramat_Gan\">Ramat Gan</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Israel\">Israel</a>, July 5-7, 2004</dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lecture_Notes_in_Computer_Science\">Lecture Notes in Computer Science</a>, Volume 3846, 2006</dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a> Berlin / Heidelberg</dd>\n<dd> ISBN 3-540-32488-7 </dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Lectures\">Lectures</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CG_2004&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Lectures\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Brian_Sheppard\" title=\"Brian Sheppard\">Brian Sheppard</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11674399_1\">Efficient Control of Selective Simulations</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2004</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Darse_Billings\" title=\"Darse Billings\">Darse Billings</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Aaron_Davidson&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Aaron Davidson (page does not exist)\">Aaron Davidson</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Terence_Schauenberg&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" t