al text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11674399_9\">Rule-Tolerant Verification Algorithms for Completeness of Chinese-Chess Endgame Databases</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2004</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ping-hsun_Wu&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ping-hsun Wu (page does not exist)\">Ping-hsun Wu</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ping-Yi_Liu&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ping-Yi Liu (page does not exist)\">Ping-Yi Liu</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11674399_10\">An External-Memory Retrograde Analysis Algorithm</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2004</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Akop_Karapetyan&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Akop Karapetyan (page does not exist)\">Akop Karapetyan</a>, <a href=\"/Richard_J._Lorentz\" title=\"Richard J. Lorentz\">Richard J. Lorentz</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11674399_11\">Generating an Opening Book for Amazons</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2004</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/David_Fotland\" title=\"David Fotland\">David Fotland</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11674399_12\">Building a World-Champion Arimaa Program</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2004</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Eli_David\" title=\"Eli David\">Omid David</a>, <a href=\"/Ariel_Felner\" title=\"Ariel Felner\">Ariel Felner</a>, <a href=\"/Nathan_S._Netanyahu\" title=\"Nathan S. Netanyahu\">Nathan S. Netanyahu</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11674399_13\">Blockage Detection in Pawn Endings</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-s