rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11674399_17\">Searching over Metapositions in Kriegspiel</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2004</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mark_Winands\" title=\"Mark Winands\">Mark Winands</a>, <a href=\"/Erik_van_der_Werf\" title=\"Erik van der Werf\">Erik van der Werf</a>, <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a>, <a href=\"/Jos_Uiterwijk\" title=\"Jos Uiterwijk\">Jos Uiterwijk</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11674399_18\">The Relative History Heuristic</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2004</a>,  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://erikvanderwerf.tengen.nl/pubdown/relhis.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Martin_M%C3%BCller\" title=\"Martin Müller\">Martin Müller</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Zhichao_Li&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Zhichao Li (page does not exist)\">Zhichao Li</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11674399_19\">Locally Informed Global Search for Sums of Combinatorial Games</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2004</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Nathan_Sturtevant\" title=\"Nathan Sturtevant\">Nathan Sturtevant</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11674399_20\">Current Challenges in Multi-player Game Search</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2004</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jouni_Smed&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jouni Smed (page does not exist)\">Jouni Smed</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Harri_Hakonen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Harri Hakonen (page does not exist)\">Harri Hakonen</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11674399_21\">Preventing Look-Ahead Cheating with Active Objects</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2004</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Joshua_Estelle&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Joshua Estelle (page does not exist)\">Joshua Estelle</a> (et al.) (<b>2004</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11674399_22\">Strategic Interactions in the TAC 2003 Supply Chain Tournament</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2004</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos\">Photos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CG_2004&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Photos\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:CG2004Conference.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"CG2004Conference.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/67/CG2004Conference.jpg/640px-CG2004Conference.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/6/67/CG2004Conference.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></div> \n<p>The conference hall, where also the players meeting of the  <a href=\"/WCCC_2004\" title=\"WCCC 2004\">WCCC</a> and <a href=\"/9th_Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"9th Computer Olympiad\">Olympiad</a> took place <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:JonathanSchaefferCG2004.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"JonathanSchaefferCG2004.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/84/JonathanSchaefferCG2004.jpg/640px-JonathanSchaefferCG2004.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/8/84/JonathanSchaefferCG2004.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></div> \n<p><a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schae